@node HISTORY "UnTAR.guide/Program history"

@{line}@{u}@{b}Author@{ub}@{uu}@{par}

@{b}37.0@{ub}	Initial release@{par}

@{b}37.1@{ub}@{lindent 8}	UnTAR now uses memory pools for most of its
memory allocations. It turned out that zlib did some temporary allocations
now and then (almost 80 for a .tgz archive on 615 kB).@{par}

Rearranged the sources a little and changed to DMake for compiling.@{par}

UnTAR is now localized, just for the fun of it. Note that zlib error
messages are not localized at the moment. Many thanks to various
@{" ATO " link "ATO.readme/MAIN"} members for their work.@{par}

Changed to zlib 1.1.3.@{par}

UnTAR will not create drawers called "." any more.@{par}@{lindent 0}

@endnode




